name: mystery
description: We wish to have a mystery in life | We wish to solve that mystery | Yet, if we solve it, we will continue to seek for a new mystery | We are interested in what extraterrestrial space ships will look like | Once we will see them we are happy to have a mystery | We hope to hear about evidence about mysteries, and how they can be explained if at all | Our body with its senses, our observational capabilities, our instincts, perception, reasoning, all need a mystery | We need a mystery | mystery
